          "45 度方向",
          "所有方向方差相同"
        ],
        "prompt": "对于一组沿 x 轴方向分布较宽、沿 y 轴方向分布较窄的二维数据，投影到哪个方向后方差最大？"
      },
      "focus_terms": [],
      "id": "s019",
      "introduced_terms": [],
      "lines": [
        "对于一组沿 x 轴方向分布较宽、沿 y 轴方向分布较窄的二维数据，投影到哪个方向后方差最大？"
      ],
      "type": "exercise"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [],
      "id": "s020",
      "introduced_terms": [],
      "lines": [
        "这个“散开的程度”就是方差。",
        "所以 PCA 的目标很直接：找到让投影后方差最大的方向。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [
        "principal_component_analysis"
      ],
      "id": "s021",
      "introduced_terms": [
        "principal_component_analysis"
      ],
      "lines": [
        "这就是<term id=\"principal_component_analysis\">主成分分析</term>（PCA）的核心思想。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [],
      "id": "s022",
      "introduced_terms": [],
      "lines": [
        "数学上，我们要找一个单位向量 \\(\\mathbf{u}\\)，",
        "使得投影后的方差 \\(\\mathbf{u}^T \\Sigma \\mathbf{u}\\) 最大。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [
        "covariance_matrix"
      ],
      "formula": {
        "latex": "\\Sigma = \\frac{1}{N} \\sum_{i=1}^{N} (\\mathbf{x}_i - \\boldsymbol{\\mu})(\\mathbf{x}_i - \\boldsymbol{\\mu})^T",
        "spoken": "协方差矩阵等于每个数据点减去均值后，乘以其转置，再取平均。"
      },
      "id": "s023",
      "introduced_terms": [
        "covariance_matrix"
      ],
      "lines": [
        "这里的 \\(\\Sigma\\) 就是数据的<term id=\"covariance_matrix\">协方差矩阵</term>。"
      ],
      "type": "formula"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [
        "eigenvector"
      ],
      "id": "s024",
      "introduced_terms": [
        "eigenvector"
      ],
      "lines": [
        "这个优化问题的答案很漂亮：",
        "使方差最大的方向，就是协方差矩阵的<term id=\"eigenvector\">特征向量</term>。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [
        "eigenvalue"
      ],
      "id": "s025",
      "introduced_terms": [
        "eigenvalue"
      ],
      "lines": [
        "对应的<term id=\"eigenvalue\">特征值</term>越大，",
        "那个方向上的方差就越大。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [],
      "id": "s026",
      "introduced_terms": [],
      "lines": [
        "所以 PCA 的步骤很简单：",
        "计算协方差矩阵 → 求特征向量 → 按特征值排序 → 取前 k 个。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
